Diagram 2 (Too Late)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par W1 is a beginner's mistake. It is based on no reading at all.
\par
\par As soon as black connects with 2, they might realize their mistake, but of course it is now too late. Black lives with a lot of points. This is a huge difference from the previous diagram.
\par }
